{
  "stem": "1062.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And when we came off the train, we-- one had to support other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We were like-- nobody could walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You know, we had like, to support each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "With the hand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We were supporting, limping along.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they took us into the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "By the camp, there is a building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they gave me a new number.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "This number was no good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "My number was like, 125,000-something, and I have the number downstairs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And they told us to go down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We're going to go for a shower.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Now, I heard stories in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I was sure this is it, because-- and we had to walk even down to the steps, and that made it even more eerie.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "There were pipes alongside there, the staircase.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And we were going down and then stairs up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And we went into a-- to a-- to a big room, big room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "There were shower heads in the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we're staying there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I recited Ashrei, my prayer and I knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Lo and behold, water is coming out, warm water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I open my mouth and I drank, you know, because you couldn't drink that water.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It was all so contaminated or something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And we got a shower.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And after we got a shower, they took-- they were outside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "They brought a big tub.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "In the tub, there was kerosene.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "One guy got a hold of the head, other guy by your feet, and they dipped you into the kerosene for disinfecting, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And I was put into a camp, into the camp, into Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "See, Buchenwald had two-- it was one big camp, but there was one camp where there was Russian prisoners of war, Norwegian.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "You know, Buchenwald was a very-- it wasn't Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
